com.paydiant.android.bluetooth.ble

Interface IBLEServiceProviderListener


  • public interface IBLEServiceProviderListener
    Defines the list of callbacks that gets invoked during the operations of IBLEServiceProvider implementation.
    Since:
    4.9.0.1
    Author:
    Paydiant

    • Method Detail

      • onDeviceDiscovery

        void onDeviceDiscovery(BLEDevice device,
                     BLEScanRecord scanRecord,
                     int rssi)
        Gets called when a remote BLE device was found during a scan.
        Parameters:
        device - - The remote BLE device found.
        scanRecord - - Remote device's advertisement data.
        rssi - - The RSSI value for the remote device as reported by the Bluetooth hardware. 0 if no RSSI value is available.

      • onDeviceDiscoveredWithPydtToken

        void onDeviceDiscoveredWithPydtToken(BLEDevice device,
                                   BLEScanRecord scanRecord,
                                   int rssi)
        Gets called only when a discovered BLE device contains Paydiant token (i.e.; "PAY:=" in device name).
        Parameters:
        device - - The remote BLE device found.
        scanRecord - - Remote device's advertisement data.
        rssi - - The RSSI value for the remote device as reported by the Bluetooth hardware. 0 if no RSSI value is available.
        Since:
        5.6.0.2

      • onDeviceConnect

        void onDeviceConnect(BLEDevice device)
        Gets called when successfully connects to a remote BLE device.
        Parameters:
        device - - connected remote BLE device.

      • onDeviceDisconnect

        void onDeviceDisconnect(BLEDevice device)
        Gets called when disconnected from a remote BLE device.
        Parameters:
        device - - remote BLE device which got disconnected.

      • onDeviceStateChanged

        void onDeviceStateChanged(int state)
        Gets called when the remote BLE device's state changed. The states can be one of IBLEServiceProvider.BLE_STATE_TURNED_ON, IBLEServiceProvider.BLE_STATE_TURNING_ON IBLEServiceProvider.BLE_STATE_TURNED_OFF or IBLEServiceProvider.BLE_STATE_TURNING_OFF values.
        Parameters:
        state - - Changed remote BLE device's state.

      • onServiceDiscovery

        void onServiceDiscovery(BLEDevice device,
                      List<BLEService> services)
        Gets called when a matching service is discovered on a remote BLE device.
        Parameters:
        device - - remote BLE Device
        services - - discovered service.

      • onCharacteristicsRead

        void onCharacteristicsRead(BLEDevice device,
                         BLEService service,
                         BLECharacteristic characteristic)
        Gets called when a characteristic from a remote BLE device is read.
        Parameters:
        device - - remote BLE Device
        service - - service the characteristic found.
        characteristic - - Read characteristic. The data of the characteristic should be accessible via BLECharacteristic.getScanRecord() method.

      • onAllCharacteristicsRead

        Gets called when all the characteristics from a remote BLE device is read.
        Parameters:

        service - - service the characteristics found.
        characteristics - - Read characteristics.
